HEADWORD: Meddler
<hw>Med"dler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who meddles; one
who interferes or busies himself with things in which he has no concern;
an officious person; a busybody.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Meddlesome</ent>⟦br⟧
